---
title: French-Inspired Chicken and Lentil Salad with Herby Goat Cheese and Walnuts
description: Satisfying and sophisticated, this chicken-topped salad makes a superb supper! Marinated lentils provide a hearty salad base and creamy, tangy goat cheese is rolled in fresh herbs for a luxurious topping!
